    "client_msg_id": "04140009-921f-4b0b-95ac-fe8a7fca7988",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Reimplement this idea using special lego blocks. The lego blocks contain electronic circuitry, so they actually implement the logic. To support copy/paste, implement reflection: There is a block that operates like the \"quote\" operator in Lisp: It constructs a value describing the construction that the Quote block is plugged in to. Then attach an Email block to the Quote block and email the program to yourself.",
